  <div><%= image_tag("crop_slime", size:"83x26", class:"ps-2") %> <small><i>FREE</i> Worker Exploitation</small></div>
  <div class="ps-2"><small>Arrives via Scamazon Shipping in <b>25 minutes</b></small></div>
